### 5 Exclusive USP Features (New Components)

#### 🧠 TiltMeter ([TiltMeter.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/components/TiltMeter.tsx))
- Reads Recoil moves store to detect blunder patterns
- Shows animated stress bar: **Calm → Shaky → Stressed → Tilting → ON TILT 🔥**
- Displays actionable tips when tilt level is high
- Integrated into Game screen sidebar

#### 🎤 AI Coach Panel ([AICoachPanel.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/components/AICoachPanel.tsx))
- Generates contextual tips after every single move
- Covers: openings (moves 1–10), castling, checks, captures, promotions, endgame
- Fully deterministic — no API key required
- Integrated into Game screen sidebar

#### ⚡ ELO Predictor ([EloPredictor.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/components/EloPredictor.tsx))
- Uses standard Elo formula (K=20) to calculate win/draw/loss ELO delta
- Shows underdog/favorite status with motivational tip
- Displayed in Game pre-game lobby

#### 🧩 Puzzles Screen ([Puzzles.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/screens/Puzzles.tsx))
- Date-seeded daily puzzle (rotates from 7-puzzle pool)
- Mini chessboard rendered with pure Unicode chess pieces
- Move input with UCI format, smart hints after 2 wrong attempts
- Streak tracker + puzzle rating display

#### 🧬 Profile Screen ([Profile.tsx](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/others/minor%20project/chess-main/apps/frontend/src/screens/Profile.tsx))
- Opening DNA donut chart (pure SVG)
- Style radar chart (5 metrics: Aggression, Accuracy, Tactics, Endgame, Openings)
- Rating history bar chart
- Achievement grid (earned/locked states)
- ELO predictor comparison table

